<jaN0001>Shuhei
<enN0001>Shuhei

///================================================================================

//TEXT
<jaT0001>Right, he's bearing a submachine gun and he's got cover from the Hamal. It's too dangerous to act when we don't know what they're planning.
<enT0001>Right, he's bearing a submachine gun and he's got cover from the Hamal. It's too dangerous to act when we don't know what they're planning.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>I signaled to the two behind me to close the fire door.
<enT0002>I signaled to the two behind me to close the fire door.

//TEXT
<jaT0003>The buzzer rang to announce its closing, and soon it began to slowly close. Then I got a bad feeling.
<enT0003>The buzzer rang to announce its closing, and soon it began to slowly close. Then I got a bad feeling.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0004>"(Why did that shield guy stop there?)"
<enT0004>"(Why did that shield guy stop there?)"

//TEXT
<jaT0005>The man put his hand to his chest and stared straight at us. He was holding something.
<enT0005>The man put his hand to his chest and stared straight at us. He was holding something.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0006>"Wait! Stop the fire door!"
<enT0006>"Wait! Stop the fire door!"

//TEXT
<jaT0007>It was already too late when I screamed. The fire door continued to close without delay, and just before it finished, the man threw a black sphere with lighting speed. I watched it all with a calm state of mind.
<enT0007>It was already too late when I screamed. The fire door continued to close without delay, and just before it finished, the man threw a black sphere with lighting speed. I watched it all with a calm state of mind.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0008>"(So that's what it was. After the fire door shuts, we'll be the only ones damaged.)"
<enT0008>"(So that's what it was. After the fire door shuts, we'll be the only ones damaged.)"

//TEXT
<jaT0009>To put up at least some resistance, I desperately tried to cover that black object. However...
<enT0009>To put up at least some resistance, I desperately tried to cover that black object. However...

//TEXT
<jaT0010>The next instant, my entire body was blown apart in a tremendous blast.
<enT0010>The next instant, my entire body was blown apart in a tremendous blast.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>......
<enT0011>......

